front.title: •The First Transport Is Away!
front.gametext: Deploy on any system (except Hoth). Target a Medium Transport at a Hoth site. When reached by target: Retrieve X Force, where X = twice the number of passengers. Relocate Utinni Effect to Hoth system. Your total power is +2 in battles at Hoth sites.
front.lore: 'When you've gotten past the energy shield, proceed directly to the rendesvouz point. Understood? Good luck!'
